Preheat oven to 350 degrees F. Cook pasta according to package directions. Place frozen broccoli in a large microwave-safe and oven-proof dish and cook for 2 minutes on HIGH. Coarsely chop cooked broccoli. Mix soup with skim milk and add to chopped broccoli. Add cooked pasta and mix. Top with bread crumbs and seasoning blend. Bake in oven for 10-15 minutes until heated through.